long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: GitCode is a chrome extension that pushes your code to GitHub when you pass all tests on a Leetcode problem. Instead of manually pushing code, GitCode automatically detects the submission success message in Leetcode and pushes the code in the editor to Github. Also, users can link an existing repo in Github to GitCode, or let GitCode create a new repo to store the submitted code.
